<td>
<p><strong class="selflink">farming</strong>, <a href="/wiki/Animal_husbandry" title="Animal husbandry">animal husbandry</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Pottery" title="Pottery">pottery</a>, <a href="/wiki/Metallurgy" title="Metallurgy">metallurgy</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wheel" title="Wheel">wheel</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Circular_ditches" title="Circular ditches" class="mw-redirect">circular ditches</a>, <a href="/wiki/Henge" title="Henge">henges</a>, <a href="/wiki/Megalith" title="Megalith">megaliths</a><br />
